<header class="">
<p class="category">
<a href="https://www.politico.com/magazine/tag/history-dept" target="_top">History Dept.</a></p>
<h1 class=" ">
<span itemprop="headline">The Congressman Who Created His Own Deep State. Really.</span>
</h1>
<p class="subhead">
When he feared communists were infiltrating America, Larry McDonald took extreme measures — building his own intelligence-gathering arm.</p>
</header>
<footer class="meta">
<div itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
<meta itemprop="name" content="Zach Dorfman" />
<meta itemprop="email" content="" />
</div>
<p class="byline">
By ZACH DORFMAN</p>
<p class="timestamp"><time itemprop="datePublished" datetime='2018-12-02T07:23-0500'>December 02, 2018</time></p>
</footer></div>
<figcaption>
<p>
| Politico Illustration/iStock/Hoover Institution</p>
</figcaption>
